            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Hic iacet Ursa quae <expan><abbr>vix</abbr><ex>it</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>n<am>n</am></abbr><ex>os</ex></expan> VII et <expan><abbr>mens</abbr><ex>es</ex></expan> X Urso<lb break="no" n="3"/>lus et Romula patres <lb n="4"/>t&amp;lt;i=E&amp;gt;t&amp;lt;u=O&amp;gt;lum posuerunt <lb n="5"/>in pace <expan><abbr>n</abbr><ex cert="low">ata</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>de</abbr><ex cert="low">posita</ex></expan> &amp;lt;I=E&amp;gt;d<expan><ex>u</ex><abbr>s</abbr></expan> A<expan><ex>u</ex><abbr>gu</abbr><ex>st</ex><abbr>as</abbr></expan> 
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Unterhalb der Inschrift Darstellung eines Christograms mit einem Rebstock zur linken und einem Baum zur rechten Seite.</p>
            </div>
